| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3889 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: be332335-af5d-51af-9f72-578dea5f3485"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
